  <h2>Migration Guide</h2>

  <h3>1. Update your config</h3>
  <pre style="background:var(--bg-alt);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;font-size:0.8rem;overflow-x:auto"><code>castor migrate --config robot.rcan.yaml
# or edit manually: rcan_version: "2.1"</code></pre>

  <h3>2. Generate and sign your firmware manifest</h3>
  <pre style="background:var(--bg-alt);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;font-size:0.8rem;overflow-x:auto"><code>castor attest generate
castor attest sign --key /path/to/robot-private.pem</code></pre>

  <h3>3. Generate and publish your SBOM</h3>
  <pre style="background:var(--bg-alt);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;font-size:0.8rem;overflow-x:auto"><code>castor sbom generate
castor sbom publish --token &lt;your-rrf-token&gt;</code></pre>

  <h3>4. Enable the authority handler</h3>
  <pre style="background:var(--bg-alt);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;font-size:0.8rem;overflow-x:auto"><code># robot.rcan.yaml
authority_handler_enabled: true
audit_retention_days: 3650</code></pre>

  <h3>5. Check your L5 status</h3>
  <pre style="background:var(--bg-alt);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;font-size:0.8rem;overflow-x:auto"><code>castor doctor --json | jq '.rcan_v21'</code></pre>

  <h3>SDK: update Role references</h3>
  <pre style="background:var(--bg-alt);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;font-size:0.8rem;overflow-x:auto"><code># Python — LevelOfAssurance is kept as an alias, but values changed
# Old: LevelOfAssurance.HARDWARE_TOKEN → New: Role.ADMIN or Role.CREATOR
from rcan.identity import Role
print(Role.ADMIN)   # 3

# TypeScript — FEDERATION_SYNC/ALERT/AUDIT removed
# Replace with canonical names: FLEET_COMMAND, FAULT_REPORT, TRANSPARENCY</code></pre>

